  "critical": false,
  "description": "Semiconductor-grade electrochemical processes: copper damascene electroplating for interconnects, anodizing (aluminum Type II/III, titanium voltage-controlled oxide), electropolishing for ultrapure surfaces, electroforming for precision microstructures, and electroless plating (ENIG for PCBs). Distinct from bulk industrial electrolysis and general metal finishing by clean room requirements, sub-micron feature control, and semiconductor process integration.",
